## Section 8: Motion & Animation Tokens

### 8.1 Easing Curves

| Name | Value | Usage |
|------|-------|-------|
| **linear** | `linear` | Constant speed, loaders |
| **ease** | `ease` | Default easing |
| **ease-in** | `ease-in` | Accelerating, exits |
| **ease-out** | `ease-out` | **Decelerating, entrances (DEFAULT)** |
| **ease-in-out** | `ease-in-out` | Smooth both ways |
| **spring** | `cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1)` | Bouncy, playful |

---

### 8.2 Duration Scale

| Name | Value (ms) | Seconds | Tailwind | Usage |
|------|------------|---------|----------|-------|
| **fast** | 150 | 0.15s | `duration-150` | Quick micro-interactions |
| **normal** | 300 | 0.3s | `duration-300` | **Standard transitions** |
| **medium** | 500 | 0.5s | `duration-500` | **Modal/drawer entrances** |
| **slow** | 700 | 0.7s | `duration-700` | Page transitions |
| **slower** | 1000 | 1s | `duration-1000` | Lazy loaders |

---

### 8.3 Delay Values

| Value (ms) | Tailwind | Usage |
|------------|----------|-------|
| 75 | `delay-75` | Micro delay |
| 150 | `delay-150` | Small delay |
| 300 | `delay-300` | Staggered animations |
| 500 | `delay-500` | Longer delay |

---

### 8.4 Keyframe Animations

#### 8.4.1 Fade In

```css
@keyframes fade-in {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}
```

**Default Duration**: 500ms
**Default Easing**: ease-out
**Tailwind Class**: `animate-fade-in`

**When to Use**:
- Modal entrances
- Toast notifications
- Content loading

**Do NOT Use**:
- Page transitions (too abrupt)
- Hover states (too slow)

**Code Example**:
```tsx
<div className="animate-fade-in">
  <p>This content fades in</p>
</div>
```

---

#### 8.4.2 Slide In Bottom

```css
@keyframes slide-in-bottom {
  0% { transform: translateY(100%); opacity: 0; }
  100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}
```

**Duration**: 500ms
**Easing**: ease-out
**Tailwind**: `animate-slide-in-bottom`

**Usage**: Drawers, bottom sheets, mobile menus

---

#### 8.4.3 Slide In Top

```css
@keyframes slide-in-top {
  0% { transform: translateY(-100%); opacity: 0; }
  100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}
```

**Duration**: 500ms
**Usage**: Top notifications, banners

---

#### 8.4.4 Scale In

```css
@keyframes scale-in {
  0% { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0; }
  100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
}
```

**Duration**: 300ms (fast)
**Usage**: Popovers, tooltips, dropdowns

---

#### 8.4.5 Bounce In

```css
@keyframes bounce-in {
  0% { transform: scale(0.3); opacity: 0; }
  50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
  70% { transform: scale(0.9); }
  100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
}
```

**Duration**: 500ms
**Usage**: Success animations, celebration effects

---

#### 8.4.6 Shimmer (Loading)

```css
@keyframes shimmer {
  0% { background-position: -200% 0; }
  100% { background-position: 200% 0; }
}
```

**Duration**: 2s
**Repeat**: Infinite
**Usage**: Skeleton loaders, loading placeholders

**Code Example**:
```tsx
<div className="animate-shimmer bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral-200 via-neutral-100 to-neutral-200 bg-[length:200%_100%]">
  <div className="h-4 rounded"></div>
</div>
```

---

#### 8.4.7 Gradient Animation

```css
@keyframes gradient {
  0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
  50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
}
```

**Duration**: 8s
**Repeat**: Infinite
**Usage**: Animated gradient backgrounds

---

#### 8.4.8 Float

```css
@keyframes float {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
}
```

**Duration**: 6s
**Repeat**: Infinite
**Usage**: Floating icons, decorative elements

---

#### 8.4.9 Glow

```css
@keyframes glow {
  0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); }
  50% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.8), 0 0 60px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4); }
}
```

**Duration**: 2s
**Repeat**: Infinite
**Usage**: Attention-grabbing elements, live indicators

---

#### 8.4.10 Levitate

```css
@keyframes levitate {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
  25% { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(-1deg); }
  75% { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(1deg); }
}
```

**Duration**: 3s
**Usage**: Floating cards, hover effects

---

### 8.5 Framer Motion Patterns

#### Standard Transition

```tsx
import { motion } from 'framer-motion';

<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0, x: 50 }}
  animate={{ opacity: 1, x: 0 }}
  exit={{ opacity: 0, x: -50 }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.5, ease: 'easeOut' }}
>
  {/* Content */}
</motion.div>
```

**Usage**: Multi-step wizards, tab panels, slide-in panels

---

#### Hover Effect

```tsx
<motion.button
  whileHover={{ scale: 1.02, y: -2 }}
  whileTap={{ scale: 0.98 }}
  transition={{ type: 'spring', stiffness: 300 }}
>
  Hover me
</motion.button>
```

---

#### Staggered Children

```tsx
<motion.div
  variants={containerVariants}
  initial="hidden"
  animate="visible"
>
  {items.map((item) => (
    <motion.div key={item.id} variants={itemVariants}>
      {item.content}
    </motion.div>
  ))}
</motion.div>

const containerVariants = {
  hidden: { opacity: 0 },
  visible: {
    opacity: 1,
    transition: {
      staggerChildren: 0.1
    }
  }
};

const itemVariants = {
  hidden: { opacity: 0, y: 20 },
  visible: { opacity: 1, y: 0 }
};
```

---

